text.section:
"Party" means:
in a guardianship case under this subtitle:
the child;
except as provided in § 5-326(a)(3)(iii) of this subtitle, the child's parent; and
the local department to which the child is committed;
in an adoption case under Part III of this subtitle:
the child;
the child's parent; and
the individual seeking adoption;
in an adoption case under Part IV of this subtitle:
the child; and
the individual seeking adoption; and
if express reference is made to a CINA case, a governmental unit or person defined as a party in § 3-801 of the Courts Article.
